dc_title_s: Situations plan von der Gegend zwischen Dresden und Pillnitz.
dc_description_s: In lower right below border: T. E. D. Topographic map showing battle information for 1778, 1782, 1788, 1802 some in ms. additions. Relief shown by hachures. 1 map: col.; 24 x 32 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
